Summer is here, and with the holiday season around the corner, there is even more reason to get behind the wheel and take in SA’s wonderful scenery. Hidden gems, rare finds, and unexpected discoveries are almost guaranteed, and spontaneity is encouraged. However, some upfront planning is necessary to make sure that your journey is as pleasant as eating an ice-cream on a hot summer's day. Now that you’re all set up, what’s the first song that will play on your road trip? We hope it’s upbeat! This article was paid for by MiWay.